Summary: I was outside with puppy, saw what looked like shooting stars coming from a shimmering star,took pics and amazing video, came to work its still there
divs: Sighting DetailsI took puppy outside before leaving for work, I looked up and seen what looked like shooting stars coming out of a shimmering star, I went and got my phone and took pics and then got a awesome video, got to work and it is still there, showed my boss and he's amazed too. It has been there long time between big dipper and moon, saucer shape spinning like with blue and red lights
